[h1]Blight hits. Your colony responds instantly.[/h1]

[b]Auto Cut Blight[/b] detects blight the moment it appears and takes immediate action. No more losing entire fields because you were busy managing a raid.

[hr][/hr]

[h1]What It Does[/h1]

[list]
[*] [b]Instant detection[/b] -- scans every 2 seconds for blighted plants
[*] [b]Auto-designate for cutting[/b] -- blighted plants marked immediately
[*] [b]Priority boost[/b] -- PlantCutting set to priority 1 for all colonists during blight
[*] [b]Block other plant work[/b] -- tree cutting, berry harvesting, and sowing are blocked until blight is cleared
[*] [b]Auto-enable manual priorities[/b] -- if you have manual priorities off, temporarily enables them so the boost works
[*] [b]Harvest -> Cut swap[/b] -- blighted plants with harvest designation auto-switch to cut
[*] [b]Sow blocking[/b] -- prevents planting new crops in blighted areas
[*] [b]Everything restores[/b] -- priorities, manual mode, sowing all return to normal when blight is cleared
[/list]

[hr][/hr]

[h1]Settings[/h1]

[list]
[*] Enable/disable auto-cut
[*] Home zone only toggle
[*] Show/hide notifications
[*] Priority boost toggle
[*] Sow blocking toggle
[/list]

[hr][/hr]

[h1]Compatibility[/h1]

[list]
[*] Works with any mod
[*] Safe to add or remove mid-save
[*] No conflicts
[/list]

[h1]Requirements[/h1]
[list]
[*] RimWorld 1.6+
[*] [url=https://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/?id=2009463077]Harmony[/url]
[/list]

[hr][/hr]

[h1]Languages[/h1]
English, German, Chinese Simplified, Japanese, Korean, Russian, Spanish

